"What happened to my computer?"
Your files are encrypted, including documents, photos, videos, databases and other files are no longer available because they have been encrypted.
"How can I recover my files?"
You need to submit a payment in 3 days in order to be able to decrypt your files. After that, the price will be doubled. Also, if you don't pay in 7 days, your files will be deleted forever.
"How do I pay?"
Payment is accepted in Monero only. For more information click <About Monero>. Please check the current price of Monero and buy some. For more information, click <How to buy Monero>. After buying, send the correct amount to the wallet address specified in this window. After your payment, click <Check Payment>.
